nodes.text: A four-eyed Jedi Master served on the Assembly of great Masters of the Jedi Order around the time of the Great Sith War. Along with Vodo-Siosk Baas, Thon, Odan-Urr, and Ood Bnar, the four-eyed being spoke with Nomi Sunrider, Qrrrl Toq, Cay Qel-Droma and Dace Diath before their mission to Empress Teta.
